             was indicted for <rs id="t18180909-301-off1654" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180909-301-off1654" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-301-off1654" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180909-301-cd1655" type="crimeDate">1st of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-301-off1654 t18180909-301-cd1655"></join>, one watch, value 30s.; one seal, value 1s.; two watch-keys, value 6d., and one piece of ribbon, value 3d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18180909-301-victim2087" type="victimName">
                  Samuel 
                  Gwilliams
               <interp inst="t18180909-301-victim2087" type="surname" value="Gwilliams"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-301-victim2087" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180909-301-victim2087" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
